<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-image-wrap">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1414235077428-338989a2e8c0?w=600&h=400&fit=crop"
        alt="Restaurant interior"
        width="600"
        height="400"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
      <h2 class="about-title">Our story</h2>
      <p>
        The story of our flavors began in the time of our great-great-grandparents. These recipes have been passed
        down from generation to generation, preserving the authentic Mexican taste that fills us with pride.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today, we are honored to bring all those traditional flavors to Vancouver, so you can enjoy a little piece of
        Mexico in every bite.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Antojitos El Rincon del Mexicano</strong><br />
        Tradition you can taste ❤️
      </p>
      <ul class="about-features">
        <li>🌽 Fresh ingredients</li>
        <li>👨‍👩‍👧 Family recipes</li>
        <li>🚚 Fast service</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .about-image-wrap {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .about-image-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-green);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  .about-features {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .about-features li {
    padding: 0.35rem 0;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
